Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没…还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 怎么样 找到面麻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然面麻已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.88,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 波波 鹤子 安鸣 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…是日记的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这字…是面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鹤子 最喜欢温柔的鹤子了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面…麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雪集 最喜欢努力的雪集了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「波波 最喜欢有趣的波波了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「安鸣 最喜欢独立的安鸣了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最喜欢仁碳了 对仁碳的喜欢 是想成为仁碳的新娘的那种最喜欢」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次终于好好地告别了 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 不找到你
