Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见你啊 面麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候 叫名字是不对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻真不擅长玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁碳 好好说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就能结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信 我们读了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜欢你了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面的不算是告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你替我实现了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳又把面麻弄哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}弄哭了弄哭啦 去向老师告状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 你这家伙居然叛变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 怎么能这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想再和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要转世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和大家…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 哭了哦 告别了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预…备…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 找到你啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻果然还是笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在慢慢长大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们走过的季节里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路旁盛开的花朵也在不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个季节盛开的花是…叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻摇曳着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一碰的话会微微刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近一闻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐约有股青涩的阳光的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那气息渐渐地淡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在慢慢长大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朵花 一定还在某个地方盛开着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们永远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会继续实现那朵花的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.64,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,146)}超和平Busters永远是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:55.12,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,300)}{\frz12}ByeBye
